3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses linear prediction, which is a common technique used in machine learning for time series analysis. 
4. cs.SI (Signal Processing) - The paper discusses a frequency domain "test-channel" realization, which is a common technique used in signal processing. 
5. cs.SP (Speech Processing) - The paper discusses linear prediction, which is a common technique used in speech processing for speech analysis and synthesis.
